it works perfectly, but i guess many users use default google api key, so it reach day limit fast, so i recommend to change it

Hi,

I change the key by a newest (from http://code.google.com/intl/en-us/apis/maps/signup.html) and it doesn't work. I need HELP !!!

For information, i make a little change in gmap.cs for search the api key in app.config:

       public string GoogleMapsAPIConfigKey = "GoogleMapsAPIKey";
       private string googleMapsAPIKey = @"ABQIAAAAWaQgWiEBF3lW97ifKnAczhRAzBk5Igf8Z5n2W3hNnMT0j2TikxTLtVIGU7hCLLHMAuAMt-BO5UrEWA";
       public string GoogleMapsAPIKey
       {
           get
           {
               string key = googleMapsAPIKey;
               if (!String.IsNullOrEmpty(ConfigurationManager.AppSettings[GoogleMapsAPIConfigKey]))
               {
                   key = ConfigurationManager.AppSettings[GoogleMapsAPIConfigKey];
               }
               return key;
           }
       }
